name: Welcome Home - Promotional Poster
description:
Each Passing Day's first poster!  A promotional poster for their debut album, Welcome Home.

Photo by Summer Schmitz

name: Welcome Home
description: Each Passing Day's debut album, Welcome Home is a collection of songs inspired by love and heartache.  Glen Starkey of the New Times says "Listening to “Homesick,” a track off of Welcome Home... by Each Passing Day, it’s easy to hear why the track won top honors at the West Coast Songwriters Competition Grand Finals in Berkeley a few weeks ago. Penned by Each Passing Day’s chief songwriter Loren Radis, the tender ballad paints a soul-drenched narrative whose power is hard to deny. It’s the second award-winning track by this young composer."
